        <br /></a>
	EQO Communications Inc has developed a revolutionary mobile service that 
keeps people connected to their online communities and instant messaging 
networks from their mobile phone. Using a combination of a proprietary 
mobile soft switch platform and a presence-enabled Voice-over-IP (VoIP) 
signaling network, EQO is capable of bridging online identity, 
presence-based calling and Instant Messaging services to mass market mobile 
handsets available worldwide.

<p>John Lieu / Francis Pang 
