        <br />
	ExxonMobil Corporation brings together a diverse and talented workforce to take on the world's toughest energy challenges. We rely on information technology to explore, develop, produce and market petroleum and petrochemical products to meet the needs of our global customer base, including our largest customer, Imperial Oil. ExxonMobil Business Support Centre Canada ULC provides both computing infrastructure and business applications support to ExxonMobil's affiliates in Canada and around the globe. As a new employee, you'll participate in a variety of challenging assignments that will test your skills in opportunity & systems analysis, troubleshooting, design, construction, testing, and implementation.  

<p>Contact Information for Campus Recruiters: 
