	Redback Networks Inc., designs, develops, and markets networking solutions for IP based services and communications. Redback's solutions enable carriers and service providers to rapidly and efficiently deploy broadband internet access, IP video, and online gaming with the SmartEdgeR product portfolio. 
Redback, has the next-generation architecture everybody is talking about; integrated Ethernet aggregation, subscriber management and full routing on top of a modular operating system.  Redback's head office is in San Jose, California.  The Burnaby design center has over 150 employees, including software designers, hardware engineers, test engineers, professional services and customers. engineers. 
