Rocket Gaming Systems designs, develops, and delivers real-time interactive electronic gaming systems for casino slot machines. RGS's product enables players in multiple gaming facilities to simultaneously compete against one another for multi-level wide area progressive jackpots. Every day, our networked, multimedia gaming systems are enjoyed by tens of thousands of players competing in real time for major progressive jackpots. 
